// Triple Laureate PvE Season 28 Lawless
//notes: (PvE / M+KB): [Tier: A], [MW: Reload Speed] [Hakke Breach Armaments] 
[Smallbore] [Flared Magwell] 
[Crystalline Corpsebloom] (also good: Graverobber) 
[Chaos Reshaped] (Also good: Trench Barrel or One-Two Punch)
Start with Smallbore for Range and Stability, ty and then add extra Stability and Reload Speed from Flared Magwell to ensure Triple Laureate is easy to keep on target and reloads sharply to keep your Guardian doing chunks of damage with this weapon.
The main perk combination of Crystalline Corpsebloom and Chaos Reshaped is only found on this weapon, which is its main draw.
It will also help it slot nicely with Stasis buffs and builds to great effect. Crystalline Corpsebloom grants a chance for a Stasis crystal to spawn when defeating an enemy.
These can be destroyed to cause extra damage or be used for cover if in a tight spot.
Chaos Reshaped is the biggest pull here as it can activate when this weapon is stowed, reaches a damage buff of 35% if in battle for longer than 22 seconds, and when hitting this,
it will also heal your character in bursts. This makes this weapon perfect for any level of content.|tags:pve,mkb
